title: Episode 322: New Vag, Who Dis? (Feat. Rip Micheals & Sevyn Streeter)
itunes:title: Episode 322: New Vag, Who Dis? (Feat. Rip Micheals & Sevyn Streeter)
description:
Comedian, Rip Micheals & Singer/songwriter Sevyn Streeter join the ladies of Lip Service this week! The crew discuss saying 'I love you' too soon, men talking sexy to women, giving men blue balls, and much more. Rip even lets Angela go through the search history on his phone! Make sure to check out Rip MIcheals "Fall Back Comedy Tour" and Sevyn's latest album "Drunk Wordz Sober Thoughts." Enjoy!
